owltools.ontologyverification.impl

Class DanglingReferenceCheck

  • java.lang.Object
    • owltools.ontologyverification.impl.AbstractCheck
      • owltools.ontologyverification.impl.DanglingReferenceCheck
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OntologyCheck

    public class DanglingReferenceCheck
extends AbstractCheck
    Check for dangling references in equivalence axioms. A reference is assumed to be dangling, if there is no declaration axiom for an OWLClass and has no annotation assertions This currently limited to OBO style ontologies.
